name: Kashyyyk Operative
Lore: 'Following the subjugation of Kashyyyk by the Empire, the Alliance hired merchants to ''purchase'' Wookiee slaves to be freed.',
Text: 'While at a Kashyyyk site: adds 1 to your Force drains there, is forfeit +1 (and power +1 if your Wookiee is on Kashyyyk) and, once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one site to Kashyyyk from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
